name: OCKAnyReadOnlyOutcomeStore
desc: A read-only custom store that fetches outcome data objects.

items.name: var outcomeDelegate: OCKOutcomeStoreDelegate?
items.desc: The object that handles callbacks from an outcome store, when the contents of the outcome store change.

items.name: func fetchAnyOutcome(query: OCKAnyOutcomeQuery, callbackQueue: DispatchQueue, completion: OCKResultClosure<OCKAnyOutcome>)
items.desc: Fetches an outcome asynchronously from the store.

items.desc: Fetches an array of outcomes asynchronously from the store.
